headline: CBRE Group, Inc. to Present at the Goldman Sachs 2024 Financial Services Conference
summary: DALLAS, December 09, 2024--CBRE (NYSE: CBRE) announced today that Bob Sulentic, the company’s chair & chief executive officer, will participate in a fireside chat at the Goldman Sachs Financial Services Conference on Wednesday, December 11, 2024. The presentation is scheduled for 8 am Eastern time.

headline: CBRE’s climate transition strategy targets supply chain, efficiency actions
summary: Measures to decarbonize include working with clients and suppliers to reduce emissions, which would help decrease its large share of scope 3 emissions, the firm says.
